  "body": "<!--NOTE: -->\r\n<!--- General questions should go to the discord chat instead of the issue tracker.-->\r\n\r\n**Describe the bug**\r\n\r\nWe parse the topic string on every gossip message to get the subnet.\r\n\r\nhttps://github.com/ChainSafe/lodestar/blob/e886a2349eea38b24ddb4df524be7d9b42fd1aab/packages/lodestar/src/network/gossip/validator.ts#L77\r\n\r\n**Expected behavior**\r\n\r\nWe could achieve the same result passing the topic and subnet to the validator function using a closure. Then no need to run a regex every message.\r\n\r\nhttps://github.com/ChainSafe/lodestar/blob/e886a2349eea38b24ddb4df524be7d9b42fd1aab/packages/lodestar/src/network/gossip/validator.ts#L120-L128",
